{"tid":2186772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南蒙古：鮮為人知的種族滅絕","createTime":"2020-09-03T07:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T12:27:55.000Z","uid":188334,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3c386b5558c11ddc4c8d46673f19123444cc7cae","tid":2186772,"uid":188334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"「在我們自己的語言裡，我們稱自己為「Uvur Mongols」，意思是「南蒙古」或「蒙古南部」。蒙古語「Uvur」一詞根本沒有「內」的意思。中國人故意歪曲「Uvur」的意思，在漢語中把它翻譯成「內」，表示在（中國）「之內」。」<br />\n<br />\n「文革期間，南蒙古至少有10萬人被殺，50萬人遭迫害。當時南蒙古的蒙族人口只有150萬，這意味著有三分之一的人口受到種族滅絕運動的影響。」<br />\n<br />\n「中共在南蒙古、西藏和東突厥斯坦實施的所有政策都經過精心設計和周密計劃，以達到徹底消滅蒙族、藏族和維族等民族的身分認同，創建一個由華人組成的無憂社會的目的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/southern-mongolia-the-unknown-cultural-genocide/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fsouthern-mongolia-the-unknown-cultural-genocide%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=81fc54e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/southern-mongolia-the-unknown-cultural-genocide/</a>"},{"pid":"6789a735bda58a38e988458b9581fbdfa0f22008","tid":2186772,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35b4524ef5fb1f403346b370687ccd57832e31e4","tid":2186772,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303cb9bddcfa2a54cf53e25dd2c086308c68a779","tid":2186772,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04ea4c2bae35ea5a2d9196cf0d0b6713dada14bb","tid":2186772,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"但支那喺南蒙真係最成功<br />\n新疆西藏全部叛亂過得佢地冇<br />\n仲要當年主要係啲南蒙兵去鎮壓佢兩個"},{"pid":"1e4b258fd5b7ef1b91fa6d3cf9e14ea6f9555318","tid":2186772,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T0